<headline>Special Weather Statement issued May 16 at 1:40PM MDT  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>Showers and thunderstorms are developing across southwest Montana
and moving northeastward through the afternoon and evening hours.
Some storms may produce erratic gusty winds up to 40 MPH.
Additionally, some storms may produce periods of heavy rain and hail.</description>
